Page 19 = 1: Vypočujte si dialog a zoraďte = Listen to the dialogue and put them in order : 1 - 6 - 3 - 2 - 7 - 5 - 4
  2: Vyberte Otázku pre formálnu komunikáciu = Select Question for formal communication : 1 - 1 - 2 - 1
  3: Opravte Chyby = Fix Errors : 1) Ako Sa Mas 2) Volam Sa Johanna Mark 3) Odikal Ste 4) Som z Slovenka 5) Nech sa páči to je kĺúč izba čísl
  45 - Ahoj. ti si Zuzana? = Hello you are Zuzana? - Ano. ja som zuzana. Ahoj. A ty Ako so volas? = Yes. I'm Zuzana. Hello. And you. How are you? 
    - Volam sa Johanna. Som tvoja spolubvyvajuca = My name is Johanna. I'm your roommate - Tesi ma. odkial si Johanna? = You make me sad. where are you from Johanna? -
    Z nemecka. A ty? = From Germany. And you? -Zo sovlenska = From Slovakia
  46 - Ahoj = Hello - Je tu Zuzana = Zuzana is here - Ano. Je = Yes. It is - Ja Som Robert = I'm Robert - Kto Je Tam = Who's There - Robert - A. To je moj brat = That's my brother -
    Ahoj Robert. Johanna. Toto je moj brat robert = Hi Robert. Johanna. This is my brother robert - tesi ma = nice to meet you - A toto je moja spolubvajuca Johanna = And this is my roommate Johanna -
    Tesi Ma. Johanna = Nice to meet you Johanna
  4: Doplnte = Supplement (complete the sentences) - answers are above
  5: Vyberte otazku pre neformalnu komunicaciu = Choose a question for informal communication (select corrrect answer for informal communcation) : ends with 's' or shorter response -not typing out
47 - Odkial si. Johanna? = where are you from Johanna? - Z Nemecka = From Germany - Co robis na Slevensku? = What are you doing in Slevensk? - Studujem tu dizajin = I study design here - 
    Dizajin? Hm. Zaujimauve = Design? Um. Interesting - a co stdujes ty? = and what are you studying? - Nestudujem. Pracujem. Som Manazer = I don't study. I'm working. I'm a Manager - 
    Nie si student? Kolko mas rokov? = Aren't you a student? How old are you? - Tridsat. A ty? = Thirty. And you? - Ja Mam Dvadsatjeden = I'm twenty-one - Hovoris dobre po slovensky = You speak Slovak well -
    Dakujem = Thank you - Ja nehovorim po nemecky = I don't speak German - Nevadi ja sa ucim po slovensky = Never mind, I'm learning Slovak
  6: pravda Alebo nepravda? = true or false? : P - P - P - P - N
  7: Oppovedajte = Answer back(answer the questions)
  8: Doplnte = Supplement (Fill in the form) : Name / Job /Age / From Where / Speaks Slovak
48 - Aha. To je robert a jeho kamart carlo. Ahoj Robert. Cau Carlo = Oh yeah. This is Robert and his friend Carlo. Hi Robert. Hello Carlo - Ahojte = Hello - Caute = Hello - 
    Johanna. Toto je moj kamarat carlo. Carlo je moj kolega = This is my friend carlo. Carlo is my colleague - Ahoj Carlo. Ja so johanna = Hi Carlo. I'm Johanna - 
    Tesi ma. Odikal si Johanna? = Nice to meet you. Did you miss Johanna? - Som z nemecka. A ty? = I'm from Germany. And you? - Z talianska = From Italy - Co robis na slovensku = What are you doing in Slovakia 
    - Pracujem. Som manazer. A co ty? studujes alebo pracujes?  = I am working. I'm a manager. What about you? are you studying or working? - studujem dizajin = I study design -
    po slovensky? = In slovak? - nie. po anglicky. ale ucim sa slencinu = no. in English. but I'm learning slovak - ja tiez = Me too
  9: Doplnte = Supplement (fill in the sentence) : Read above
  10: Doplnte Otazky = Complete the questions : Where do you live / What do you do / What are you studying / something about language / where are you from
Page 23 = Kto je kto? = Who is who? (Muz = Male vs Zena = female) :
Pan = Mr. Vs Pani(Dama) = Lady / Pan Vs Slecna = Miss / Chlapec = Boy vs Dievca = Girl / Brat = Brother vs Sestra = Sister / Splubyvajuci = Couple Vs Splubyvajuca = Couple / Kolega = Colleague vs Kolegyna = Colleague
priatel = Boyfriend vs priatelka = Girlfriend / ucitel vs ucitelka = Teacher / student vs studentka = Student / manazer vs manazerka = Manager  
  11: Doplnte = Supplement (fill in the ending of word) : profesorka / ministerka / prezidentka / sefka / lektorka
  12: Doplnte = Supplement (fill in the ending) : 
    Not Married male = Robert Soltys -> Robert je Slobodny = robert is single / Not Married Female = Johanna Mark -> johanna slobodna = Johanna is single 
    Married Male = Peter Vrana -> Peter je zenaty = peter is married + peter vrana je manzel = peter vrana is a husband
    Married Female = Eva Vranova -> Eva je vydata = Eva is married  + Pani vranova je manzelka = Eva is a wife
Page 24 = Personalne Pronomina = Personal Pronouns :
Male = Ends with 'y' / Female = Ends with 'a'
Singular Vs Plural : Ja Vs My / Ty vs Vy / on+ona+ono Vs Oni+Ony
  13:Doplnte Tv/Vy = Supplement Ty(Singular-informal) or Vy(Plural-formal) : 1) Ty - 2) Ty 3) Vy 4) Ty 5) Ty
  14: Doplnte Oni/Ony = Supplement(fill in) Oni(Plural+ >2+) or Ony(Plural ~2) : 1) Ony 2) ony 3) oni 4) oni
  15: Doplnte (Fill in the blanks) : 
